'''卡迭石战役'''是[[古埃及|古埃及]]与[[赫梯王国|赫梯王国]]争夺[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]地区统治权而发生的[[战役|战役]]。

约前1274年5月底[[埃及第十九王朝|埃及第十九王朝]]的法老[[拉美西斯二世|拉美西斯二世]]与赫梯国王在[[奥伦特河|奥伦特河]]边的卡迭石（[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]的[[大马士革|大马士革]]东北）会战，初期法老失利，第二天再战，赫梯受挫。双方均未取得决定性胜利。<ref name="Eggenberger">{{cite book|title=An Encyclopedia of Battles|url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofba00egge|url-access=registration|first=David|last=Eggenberger|year=1985|publisher=Dover Publications|page=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofba00egge/page/214 214]|isbn=9780486249131}}</ref><ref name="Parragon">{{cite book|author=Dr. Aaron Ralby|title=Atlas of Military History|chapter-url=https://archive.org/details/atlasofworldmili0000ralb|chapter-url-access=registration|year=2013|publisher=Parragon|isbn=978-1-4723-0963-1|pages=[https://archive.org/details/atlasofworldmili0000ralb/page/54 54–55]|chapter=Battle of Kadesh, c. 1274 BCE: Clash of Empires}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Dr. Aaron Ralby|title=Atlas of Military History|chapter-url=https://archive.org/details/atlasofworldmili0000ralb|chapter-url-access=registration|year=2013|publisher=Parragon|isbn=978-1-4723-0963-1|pages=[https://archive.org/details/atlasofworldmili0000ralb/page/52 52–53]|chapter=Hatti and Mitanni, 18th–12th Centuries BCE: A Kingdom Found}}</ref>

约前1258年，赫梯王国的國王病逝，新任國王[[哈杜西勒三世|哈杜西勒三世]]繼位，两国缔结《[[埃及赫梯和約|埃及赫梯和約]]》，成为军事同盟。{{sfn| Ockinga|1987|p=38|ps=: "No battle fought in antiquity is so well-documented as the clash between the Egyptians and the Hittites before the city of Kadesh on the Orontes in 1275 BC"}}

